        <item>
            <title>
                <![CDATA[说好的数位黄金避险呢？以巴冲突后盘点各类资产表现]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>巴勒斯坦激进组织哈马斯在周末袭击以色列后，以色列誓言「全面围堵」，已演变为全面战争。此段时间投资人涌入美国公债和黄金避险，连美股都摆脱九月魔咒，连续三天上涨。但以数位黄金著称的比特币似乎没有出现大幅的买盘，而以太币则是因以太坊基金会卖币的影响，此期间下跌了近 3%。</p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_56_1 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">内容目录</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/assets-performance-after-hamas-attack#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-65266b813773f"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list-377408" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999" class="arrow-unsorted-368013"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-65266b813773f"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/assets-performance-after-hamas-attack/#%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E4%BA%BA%E6%B9%A7%E5%85%A5%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%82%B5%E5%92%8C%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E9%81%BF%E9%9A%AA" title="投资人涌入美国公债和黄金避险">投资人涌入美国公债和黄金避险</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/assets-performance-after-hamas-attack/#%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E9%80%A3%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2%EF%BC%8C%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A" title="美股连三天上涨，投资者持续关注经济数据">美股连三天上涨，投资者持续关注经济数据</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E4%BA%BA%E6%B9%A7%E5%85%A5%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%82%B5%E5%92%8C%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E9%81%BF%E9%9A%AA"></span>投资人涌入美国公债和黄金避险<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>由于投资者在以色列与哈马斯战争期间蜂拥避险，美国公债殖利率周二下跌。10 年期公债殖利率下跌约 10 个基点至 4.645%，2 年期公债殖利率跌破 5 % 水平，收在 4.967%。由于收益率与价格成反比，这意味著债券价格在避险需求的推动下上涨。</p><p>链新闻统计了自 10/6 凌晨至昨日收盘价 (若无收盘者以今日台湾时间九点价格为依据) ，发现除了美国公债之外，黄金作为避险工具也上涨了近 2%，而受产地地缘风险的影响，原油价格上涨了 4.29%。但加密货币，尤其是以数位黄金著称的比特币，此次似乎没有出现大幅的买盘，而以太币则是因以太坊基金会卖币的影响，表现最为逊色，此期间下跌了近 3%。</p><p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-80540" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/%E5%9C%96%E7%89%87_2023-10-11_095438169.png?resize=1429%2C604&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="1429" height="604" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/图片_2023-10-11_095438169.png?w=1429&amp;ssl=1 1429w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/图片_2023-10-11_095438169.png?resize=300%2C127&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/图片_2023-10-11_095438169.png?resize=1024%2C433&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/图片_2023-10-11_095438169.png?resize=600%2C254&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/图片_2023-10-11_095438169.png?resize=768%2C325&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>(<a href="https://abmedia.io/ethereum-foundation-sold-1700-eth" target="_blank" rel="noopener">以巴冲突导致油价上涨，以太坊基金会卖币 ETH 大跌</a>)</p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E9%80%A3%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2%EF%BC%8C%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A"></span>美股连三天上涨，投资者持续关注经济数据<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>而美股则是摆脱了九月魔咒，连续三天上涨，S&amp;P 500 和 Nasdaq 指数本周都有超过 2% 的涨幅。</p><p>今晚将公布的 9 月份生产者物价指数 (PPI) 和周四的消费者物价指数 (CPI)，都是投资者关注的焦点，毕竟在升息的尾端，一连串加息是否已传导到经济层面？联准会口中的「Higher for longer」又将会持续多久？又或者在潜在利率上升和地缘政治动荡的情况下，美国国债等更安全的资产是否更有意义？都是投资者需要考量的问题。</p><p>虽然九月底公布的<a href="https://abmedia.io/fomc-keep-interest-rate-unchanged" target="_blank" rel="noopener">利率点阵图显示</a>，今年底联准会可能再升息一次。但以目前芝商所 FedWatch 数据看来，投资人普遍认为九月已是升息的最后一次，但降息可能要等到明年六月以后。</p><figure id="attachment_80536" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-80536" style="width: 535px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img class="wp-image-80536 size-full" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/%E5%9C%96%E7%89%87_2023-10-11_093757402.png?resize=535%2C274&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="535" height="274" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/图片_2023-10-11_093757402.png?w=535&amp;ssl=1 535w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/图片_2023-10-11_093757402.png?resize=300%2C154&amp;ssl=1 300w" sizes="(max-width: 535px) 100vw, 535px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><figcaption id="caption-attachment-80536" class="wp-caption-text">资料来源：芝商所 CME</figcaption></figure>
]]>
            </description>
